2>
<p>Before you begin, ensure you have:</p>
<ul>
<li>Docker Engine (version 19.03.0+)</li>
<li>Docker Compose (version 1.27.0+)</li>
<li>2+ CPU cores and 4GB+ RAM</li>
<li>At least 20GB free disk space</li>
<li>Basic understanding of Docker concepts</li>
</ul>
