<p>Grafana supports automatic setup through provisioning.</p>
<ul>
<li>In <code>datasource.yml</code>, we define Prometheus as the default dat=
a source using the internal Docker URL.</li>
<li>In <code>dashboards.yml</code>, we tell Grafana to load dashboards from=
 a specific folder.</li>
<li>The <code>grafana/dashboards</code> directory is where you=E2=80=99ll s=
tore those dashboard JSON files.</li>
</ul>
<p>With this setup, Grafana connects to Prometheus and loads dashboards aut=
omatically=E2=80=94no manual steps needed.</p>
